---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions | Wise Energy Pros" description="Terms and Conditions for Wise Energy Pros website and service requests." lang="en">
	<section class="bg-slate-950 py-20">
		<div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-50 md:text-5xl">Terms and Conditions</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 text-slate-400">Effective date: March 20, 2026</p>
			<p class="mt-6 text-slate-400">
				These Terms and Conditions govern your use of the Wise Energy Pros website and any service inquiries submitted through our digital channels. By accessing this website, you agree to these terms.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">1. Website Use</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				The website is provided for informational purposes and to request electrical services. You agree to use it lawfully and avoid activities that interfere with security, availability, or normal operation.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">2. Service Information</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				Content, service descriptions, and examples are general guidance. Final scope, scheduling, pricing, materials, and deliverables are defined only in written proposals, estimates, or signed agreements.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">3. Estimates and Project Approval</h2>
			<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-slate-400">
				<li>Submitting a form or calling us does not create a binding service contract.</li>
				<li>Projects may require site inspection, load review, permitting, and code compliance checks.</li>
				<li>Work begins only after formal acceptance of proposal terms.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">4. Customer Responsibilities</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">Customers are responsible for providing accurate information and reasonable site access. Delays or additional work caused by hidden conditions, prior non-compliant work, or restricted access may affect schedule and cost.</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">5. Scheduling and Availability</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				Service windows, response times, and project timelines are estimates and may change due to weather, permit timelines, utility coordination, material availability, or safety conditions.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">6. Payments and Pricing</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				Payment terms are defined in each proposal or invoice. Taxes, permit fees, utility-related costs, and approved change orders may be billed according to project terms.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">7. Warranties and Limitations</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				Any workmanship warranty is limited to what is stated in writing. To the extent permitted by law, Wise Energy Pros is not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages, including downtime, lost profits, or third-party system failures.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">8. Intellectual Property</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				Website content, branding, and visual materials are owned by Wise Energy Pros or used with permission. Reproduction, redistribution, or commercial reuse without written authorization is prohibited.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">9. Third-Party Services and Links</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				This website may reference third-party platforms or embedded tools. Wise Energy Pros is not responsible for third-party content, policies, or service availability.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">10. Governing Law</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				These terms are governed by applicable laws in the State of Utah, without regard to conflict-of-law rules, unless otherwise required by law.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">11. Changes to Terms</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				We may update these Terms and Conditions from time to time. Updated terms become effective when posted on this page.
			</p>

			<h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-50">12. Contact</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-400">
				For questions regarding these terms, contact us at
				<a href="mailto:intake@wiseenergypros.com" class="font-medium text-cyan-300 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-cyan-200">intake@wiseenergypros.com</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
